# Frontend Rules (pointer)

Use **@frontend** when working on UI, pages, components, or styling.

Canonical bundles: use `@nextjs` + `@react` + `@tailwind` (or `@rules/styling/*`). For the full reference list (route handlers, server actions, data fetching, forms, Tailwind, optional integrations), see `@rules/nextjs.mdc` and `@rules/react.mdc`.

- Server Components by default; `'use client'` only when needed.
- One component/hook per file; types in `types/`; helpers in `utils/`.
